show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा

show.description: Lucilia drops a bombshell pregnancy announcement, unleashing a storm of deceit and turmoil. As she demands Ricardo acknowledge their unborn child, he pushes back with doubts about the baby's paternity. The stakes escalate when Jeremy, Lucilia's ex-boyfriend, walks free from prison after Ricardo is forced into dropping the charges against him. Meanwhile, Ricardo's marriage hangs by a thread when his wife uncovers a suspicious $10 million payment to Lucilia. Caught in a dangerous triangle of desire, money, and power, Lucilia's manipulative games begin to unravel as jealousy poisons her rekindled relationship with Jeremy. In this high-stakes battle of wills, no one will emerge unscathed.
